WEBVTT

00:00:30.480 --> 00:00:31.860
You...

00:00:32.480 --> 00:00:33.780
Me?

00:00:34.400 --> 00:00:35.940
I can't get out of character.

00:00:56.440 --> 00:00:57.500
Cut!

00:02:38.533 --> 00:02:42.735
[Episode 1]

00:02:42.735 --> 00:02:46.840
[Magic City 2026]

00:03:05.680 --> 00:03:08.600
Hello, is this the audition for Deep In?

00:03:08.600 --> 00:03:09.600
Hello.

00:03:09.600 --> 00:03:12.080
Are you Mr. Zhang Zhun, here for the audition?

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:14.220
- Yes, that's me. - This way, please.

00:03:28.240 --> 00:03:29.560
This one's not bad.

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:31.540
Cut! That's enough.

00:03:34.480 --> 00:03:35.480
Director.

00:03:35.480 --> 00:03:37.900
This is Mr. Zhang Zhun, here for the audition.

00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:40.720
Hello, Director Chen.

00:03:40.720 --> 00:03:41.880
My name is Zhang Zhun.

00:03:41.880 --> 00:03:43.760
I'm a student at Huxin Academy of Dramatic Arts.

00:03:43.760 --> 00:03:45.200
I'm currently signed with Starry Entertainment.

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:46.440
I have experience as a stunt double.

00:03:46.440 --> 00:03:49.440
A small face and a youthful look.

00:03:49.440 --> 00:03:52.360
It doesn't match your actual age.

00:03:52.360 --> 00:03:54.400
Director Chen, if the role requires it,

00:03:54.400 --> 00:03:56.440
I can also appear more mature.

00:03:56.440 --> 00:03:58.120
No need.

00:03:58.120 --> 00:04:01.880
For this character, you're a great fit physically.

00:04:01.880 --> 00:04:03.760
But...

00:04:03.760 --> 00:04:05.560
I want you to be more arrogant.

00:04:05.560 --> 00:04:09.200
You need to be beautiful, stoic, and neurotic.

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:13.200
Because this character wears fine suits and drive nice cars.

00:04:13.200 --> 00:04:16.140
Director, are we done yet?

00:04:17.320 --> 00:04:19.458
My lips are numb from all the kissing.

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:44.340
Zhen, do you want some water?

00:04:45.280 --> 00:04:47.800
Are we actually casting,

00:04:47.800 --> 00:04:50.880
Or is this a crash course for straight actors to go gay for fame?

00:04:50.880 --> 00:04:54.240
Their gazes say they're clocking in for work.

00:04:54.240 --> 00:04:56.360
The kissing is giving me a workplace injury.

00:04:56.360 --> 00:04:58.040
Throwing a tantrum again?

00:04:58.040 --> 00:05:01.520
You're just like Madam Qin when she was young.

00:05:01.520 --> 00:05:05.205
Mr. Zhen, this is Mr. Zhang Zhun, here for the audition.

00:05:06.280 --> 00:05:08.020
Hello, Mr. Zhen. We meet again.

00:05:08.920 --> 00:05:10.080
Have we met before?

00:05:10.080 --> 00:05:12.400
Oh, it's been about seven or eight years.

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:13.760
It's normal that you don't remember.

00:05:13.760 --> 00:05:15.880
I was the female lead's stunt double in Gallop.

00:05:15.880 --> 00:05:19.960
So, the female lead's stunt work isn't enough for you anymore?

00:05:19.960 --> 00:05:22.383
Now you want to try for the male lead...

00:05:23.926 --> 00:05:25.622
Romantically?

00:05:29.640 --> 00:05:32.202
Mr. Zhen, so you two are acquainted.

00:05:32.202 --> 00:05:34.960
When you debuted as the second lead in "North Peak,"

00:05:34.960 --> 00:05:38.080
The female thief you chased down the whole street...

00:05:38.080 --> 00:05:39.400
That was him.

00:05:39.400 --> 00:05:42.000
I don't remember any of that.

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:43.840
Director Chen.

00:05:43.840 --> 00:05:46.000
What are we testing this time?

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:47.740
An intimate scene.

00:05:52.200 --> 00:05:54.520
Then let's begin.

00:05:54.520 --> 00:05:55.720
Wait, Director Chen.

00:05:55.720 --> 00:05:57.600
Could Mr. Zhen and I...

00:05:57.600 --> 00:05:59.630
Go prepare for a moment?

00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:03.520
Ten minutes.

00:06:03.520 --> 00:06:05.456
- Go ahead. - Okay.

00:06:36.280 --> 00:06:37.960
Sorry, I don't know how to do this.

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:41.427
The character in the script does.

00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:05.960
Mr. Zhen, I've thought of a few ideas...

00:07:05.960 --> 00:07:08.599
If you can't keep up, then get lost.

00:07:16.880 --> 00:07:18.151
Fine.

00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:20.440
Let's start then.

00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:21.615
Wait.

00:07:22.480 --> 00:07:24.040
I'm not ready yet.

00:07:24.040 --> 00:07:25.985
Never filmed an intimate scene before?

00:07:25.985 --> 00:07:28.176
No, not this kind.

00:07:29.960 --> 00:07:31.552
Then...

00:07:36.120 --> 00:07:37.962
Let's just try it.

00:07:47.040 --> 00:07:48.600
Aren't we going to discuss the roles?

00:07:48.600 --> 00:07:50.320
What's there to discuss?

00:07:50.320 --> 00:07:52.040
We don't necessarily have to kiss.

00:07:52.040 --> 00:07:54.320
Hugging would work, too.

00:07:54.320 --> 00:07:55.480
Director.

00:07:55.480 --> 00:07:57.920
Is just hugging okay?

00:07:57.920 --> 00:07:59.440
No.

00:07:59.440 --> 00:08:00.960
There are at least three sex scenes.

00:08:00.960 --> 00:08:02.600
Two are fully nude.

00:08:02.600 --> 00:08:03.960
And no clearing the set.

00:08:03.960 --> 00:08:05.240
You heard him.

00:08:05.240 --> 00:08:06.888
No hugging.

00:08:09.280 --> 00:08:11.320
Director, we're ready.

00:08:11.320 --> 00:08:13.080
Are you messing with me?

00:08:13.080 --> 00:08:15.398
You're ready, but I'm not.

00:08:16.120 --> 00:08:17.492
Then I'll...

00:08:18.720 --> 00:08:20.630
Help you out a bit more.

00:08:32.880 --> 00:08:35.480
Keep the audition footage of these few people.

00:08:35.480 --> 00:08:37.123
Yes, Director.

00:08:39.840 --> 00:08:42.150
<i>Stop squirming. We're filming.</i>

00:08:44.200 --> 00:08:45.630
Action!

00:08:47.480 --> 00:08:50.158
<i>More tension and emotion.</i>

00:09:08.120 --> 00:09:10.020
<i>Just pretend it's Dan Yi's tongue.</i>

00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:12.480
<i>But...</i>

00:09:12.480 --> 00:09:14.451
<i>Dan Yi doesn't smoke.</i>

00:09:15.080 --> 00:09:16.880
Mr. Zhen did even better this time.

00:09:16.880 --> 00:09:18.644
As expected of a Best Actor.

00:09:19.440 --> 00:09:21.560
Xiao Zhang is still a bit lacking.

00:09:49.280 --> 00:09:51.280
Yes, yes, just like that.

00:09:51.280 --> 00:09:53.530
Keep going, keep going.

00:10:45.680 --> 00:10:47.320
Not bad. They got into character quickly.

00:10:47.320 --> 00:10:49.092
It's getting better and better.

00:10:51.840 --> 00:10:53.000
Cut!

00:10:53.000 --> 00:10:54.973
That's more like it.

00:11:08.320 --> 00:11:10.190
The restroom is over there.

00:11:12.680 --> 00:11:14.440
Not bad. You have great couple chemistry.

00:11:14.440 --> 00:11:16.440
The dynamic is excellent.

00:11:16.440 --> 00:11:17.600
Mr. Zhen.

00:11:17.600 --> 00:11:21.090
When the curtains were drawn, what were you two doing?

00:11:36.800 --> 00:11:38.560
Here's the list for the next scene.

00:11:38.560 --> 00:11:39.973
Got it.

00:11:45.480 --> 00:11:46.640
Pack everything up.

00:11:46.640 --> 00:11:48.000
It's almost time to wrap up.

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:49.520
Oh, okay.

00:11:49.520 --> 00:11:52.280
Send me your location. I'll pick you up in a bit.

00:11:52.280 --> 00:11:54.160
Hold on. Mr. Zhang, well...

00:11:54.160 --> 00:11:56.240
The director and Mr. Zhen went to meet the producer.

00:11:56.240 --> 00:11:59.000
So, your audition for today is over.

00:11:59.000 --> 00:12:01.880
If you're selected, the crew will send you a message.

00:12:01.880 --> 00:12:03.040
Okay, thank you.

00:12:03.040 --> 00:12:04.320
- Good work. - I'll head out then.

00:12:04.320 --> 00:12:07.320
Sure. By the way...

00:12:07.320 --> 00:12:09.040
Wait a second. I'll pick you up in a bit.

00:12:09.040 --> 00:12:11.263
Okay, sure. Just a moment.

00:12:43.915 --> 00:12:46.718
[Xie Dan Yi]

00:12:49.840 --> 00:12:52.040
<i>- Hello, Zhun.</i> - You're still up?

00:12:52.040 --> 00:12:54.920
<i>I couldn't sleep without your report.</i>

00:12:54.920 --> 00:12:56.880
<i>How was it? Are you home yet?</i>

00:12:56.880 --> 00:12:58.560
Not yet.

00:12:58.560 --> 00:12:59.680
<i>It's so late.</i>

00:12:59.680 --> 00:13:02.400
Pang called me on my way home.

00:13:02.400 --> 00:13:04.800
He said a friend was coming to the warehouse for props.

00:13:04.800 --> 00:13:06.360
He's busy on set and can't leave.

00:13:06.360 --> 00:13:08.523
So, I came over to help him out.

00:13:09.160 --> 00:13:11.020
<i>You really are a good guy.</i>

00:13:11.680 --> 00:13:13.640
<i>How did it go today?</i>

00:13:13.640 --> 00:13:16.500
Judging by the director's feedback, it should be okay.

00:13:17.160 --> 00:13:19.240
But there were a lot of people auditioning.

00:13:19.240 --> 00:13:21.760
I still have to wait for the results.

00:13:21.760 --> 00:13:22.880
<i>It doesn't matter.</i>

00:13:22.880 --> 00:13:24.173
<i>It's better if they choose someone else.</i>

00:13:24.173 --> 00:13:26.970
<i>I don't want men hitting on you every day.</i>

00:13:27.720 --> 00:13:30.160
Who would want to hit on an old guy like me?

00:13:30.160 --> 00:13:32.462
<i>You'd be surprised.</i>

00:13:33.320 --> 00:13:36.160
<i>My parents called me again today.</i>

00:13:36.160 --> 00:13:38.650
<i>They asked when you'd meet my family.</i>

00:13:39.720 --> 00:13:41.240
<i>Zhun.</i>

00:13:41.240 --> 00:13:43.280
<i>I don't want to pressure you.</i>

00:13:43.280 --> 00:13:46.400
<i>But at my age...</i>

00:13:46.400 --> 00:13:47.996
Dan Yi.

00:13:49.240 --> 00:13:50.940
Let me try one more time.

00:13:51.760 --> 00:13:53.400
This year.

00:13:53.400 --> 00:13:55.200
If it still doesn't work out,

00:13:55.200 --> 00:13:57.541
I'll consider giving up on acting.

00:13:59.400 --> 00:14:02.080
The person for the props is here.

00:14:02.080 --> 00:14:03.420
I'll hang up now.

00:14:04.120 --> 00:14:05.340
<i>Bye.</i>

00:15:08.440 --> 00:15:17.280
I've just lost my youthful spirit.

00:15:17.280 --> 00:15:33.720
And gray hair is already at my temples.

00:15:48.960 --> 00:15:50.040
Lin.

00:15:50.040 --> 00:15:53.300
Thanks for the audition recommendation.

00:15:59.600 --> 00:16:02.760
But could you please put in a good word for me?

00:16:02.760 --> 00:16:04.580
I really need this opportunity.

00:16:08.600 --> 00:16:10.506
[But could you please put in a good word for me?]

00:16:10.506 --> 00:16:12.400
[I really need this opportunity.]

00:16:12.400 --> 00:16:14.280
Dating is fine.

00:16:14.280 --> 00:16:16.360
Just hide it better.

00:16:16.360 --> 00:16:17.840
Look at how many endorsements we've lost.

00:16:17.840 --> 00:16:19.513
Does he want to quit the industry?

00:16:20.800 --> 00:16:22.880
Legal letters are useless.

00:16:22.880 --> 00:16:26.040
Tell him again, the company forbids internal dating.

00:16:26.040 --> 00:16:27.845
Stop looking for trouble.

00:16:33.760 --> 00:16:36.640
- Qin, sir. - How many times have I told you?

00:16:36.640 --> 00:16:38.275
It's Madam Qin.

00:16:39.040 --> 00:16:40.060
Ma'am!

00:16:42.400 --> 00:16:44.240
I don't quite understand.

00:16:44.240 --> 00:16:46.480
Director Chen's gay art film...

00:16:46.480 --> 00:16:49.680
Is basically a stepping stone and a petridish for a new couples.

00:16:49.680 --> 00:16:52.720
How did this spot fall to Zhang Zhun?

00:16:52.720 --> 00:16:54.840
My goodness.

00:16:54.840 --> 00:16:56.800
Isn't it good that he chose an artist under your management?

00:16:56.800 --> 00:16:58.280
It is.

00:16:58.280 --> 00:16:59.920
But...

00:16:59.920 --> 00:17:03.320
How can such a good thing just fall from the sky?

00:17:03.320 --> 00:17:05.080
Zhang Zhun doesn't have the star factor.

00:17:05.080 --> 00:17:07.960
The company gave up on him long ago because he couldn't be promoted.

00:17:07.960 --> 00:17:10.054
And this time...

00:17:10.054 --> 00:17:11.222
[Zhang Zhun]

00:17:15.320 --> 00:17:17.499
Zhen Xin was the one who chose him.

00:17:18.800 --> 00:17:21.412
Stop joking, ma'am. How is that possible?

00:17:33.360 --> 00:17:34.920
What a long face.

00:17:34.920 --> 00:17:36.445
Got scolded again?

00:17:38.600 --> 00:17:39.760
The thread bashing me...

00:17:39.760 --> 00:17:41.640
Already has over a thousand comments.

00:17:41.640 --> 00:17:42.800
He said, "Do it if you can."

00:17:42.800 --> 00:17:44.280
"If not, get lost."

00:17:44.280 --> 00:17:46.600
The assault incident on set was really a misunderstanding.

00:17:46.600 --> 00:17:47.880
Didn't I already explain it?

00:17:47.880 --> 00:17:49.240
All right.

00:17:49.240 --> 00:17:51.920
My dear... that's all in the past now.

00:17:51.920 --> 00:17:54.023
Come on, pick one.

00:17:56.480 --> 00:17:57.920
What do you mean?

00:17:57.920 --> 00:18:00.720
I've secured the lead role in Chen Zheng Sen's film for you.

00:18:00.720 --> 00:18:03.160
The co-star hasn't been decided yet.

00:18:03.160 --> 00:18:05.400
These are all actors from our company.

00:18:05.400 --> 00:18:06.640
See if anyone catches your eye.

00:18:06.640 --> 00:18:08.502
I'll recommend them for the screen test.

00:18:17.320 --> 00:18:20.480
You want me to carry a rookie, so they can leech off my fame?

00:18:20.480 --> 00:18:22.997
Oh, come on.

00:18:24.680 --> 00:18:26.520
You're already so famous.

00:18:26.520 --> 00:18:29.520
Don't be so petty with me.

00:18:29.520 --> 00:18:31.240
I know you're only in your twenties...

00:18:31.240 --> 00:18:33.840
And have a bright future as a newly crowned Best Actor.

00:18:33.840 --> 00:18:37.160
What the company is doing... is a bit much.

00:18:37.160 --> 00:18:41.480
But it's normal to want to cash in on the hype.

00:18:41.480 --> 00:18:42.560
Just think of it...

00:18:42.560 --> 00:18:44.680
As compensation for all the years I've slaved away for you.

00:18:44.680 --> 00:18:45.680
How about it?

00:18:45.680 --> 00:18:47.740
Come on, pick one.

00:19:03.803 --> 00:19:05.651
[Zhang Zhun]

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:15.419
Here.

00:19:19.400 --> 00:19:20.860
Are you sure?

00:19:22.080 --> 00:19:23.640
Choose carefully.

00:19:23.640 --> 00:19:25.921
What kind of ugly boy did you pick?

00:19:30.840 --> 00:19:32.081
No.

00:19:32.081 --> 00:19:33.280
[Zhang Zhun]

00:19:33.280 --> 00:19:34.597
I want him.

00:19:37.760 --> 00:19:41.061
I don't know why Zhen Xin chose him.

00:19:42.280 --> 00:19:44.939
They don't have any history, do they?

00:19:47.600 --> 00:19:50.570
Could he have offended Zhen Xin before?

00:19:51.840 --> 00:19:55.469
Then this "ugly boy" is in for a rough time on set.

00:19:56.120 --> 00:19:59.657
But it really is a great opportunity.

00:20:00.426 --> 00:20:03.512
Well then, good luck to you both.

00:20:12.960 --> 00:20:15.895
Got the beef rolls.

00:20:20.200 --> 00:20:22.547
And your favorite mushroom beef sauce.

00:20:23.680 --> 00:20:26.947
<i>Beef rolls... Mushroom beef sauce...</i>

00:20:26.947 --> 00:20:28.425
<i>That should be everything.</i>

00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:31.240
<i>Actually, besides the hot pot...</i>

00:20:31.240 --> 00:20:33.562
Dan Yi, I passed the audition!

00:20:33.562 --> 00:20:35.806
<i>Really? That's wonderful!</i>

00:20:35.806 --> 00:20:37.240
<i>- We have to celebrate tonight!</i> - I can't.

00:20:37.240 --> 00:20:38.480
There's no time.

00:20:38.480 --> 00:20:40.200
The crew said I have to join them tomorrow.

00:20:40.200 --> 00:20:41.560
I have to fly to Coconut City right away.

00:20:41.560 --> 00:20:43.120
- Dan Yi... <i>- I understand.</i>

00:20:43.120 --> 00:20:45.360
<i>Don't worry about me. I won't go hungry.</i>

00:20:45.360 --> 00:20:47.160
<i>- Go back and pack your things.</i> - Okay.

00:20:47.160 --> 00:20:49.040
I'll have the groceries delivered to you.

00:20:49.040 --> 00:20:50.040
I owe you that hot pot.

00:20:50.040 --> 00:20:52.600
When I'm done filming, I'll make it up to you.

00:20:52.600 --> 00:20:54.526
<i>Okay, I'll be waiting.</i>

00:20:55.920 --> 00:20:57.522
Just scan here.

00:21:00.080 --> 00:21:01.920
Do you need a bag? [Expense: 163, Remaining balance: 1,735.85.]

00:21:01.920 --> 00:21:04.039
- No, thanks. - All right.

00:21:05.387 --> 00:21:08.800
- This is yours too, right? - Yes, all of these.

00:21:08.800 --> 00:21:09.920
I have a membership.

00:21:09.920 --> 00:21:11.460
Can you scan it for points?

00:21:16.750 --> 00:21:19.386
Sure thing. Okay, I understand.

00:21:19.386 --> 00:21:20.560
Right, I see.

00:21:20.560 --> 00:21:22.180
Okay, thanks for your hard work.

00:21:23.000 --> 00:21:24.680
I'll follow up with them.

00:21:24.680 --> 00:21:26.168
Sure, okay.

00:21:36.320 --> 00:21:38.585
And about that project we discussed...

00:21:38.585 --> 00:21:40.520
Is it a go? [Food's here, but I'm worried about you]

00:21:40.520 --> 00:21:42.560
Then it's fine. No big deal. [Full story behind Zhen Xin on-set assault]

00:21:42.560 --> 00:21:44.220
Okay. Thanks for your hard work.

00:21:44.840 --> 00:21:46.612
This works. Okay.

00:21:46.612 --> 00:21:47.680
Let's leave it at that.

00:21:48.920 --> 00:21:49.920
Cut!

00:21:49.920 --> 00:21:51.280
Zhen Xin, that was a perfect take.

00:21:51.280 --> 00:21:52.983
That's a wrap for today.

00:22:24.320 --> 00:22:26.018
Good work, Mr. Zhen.

00:22:28.926 --> 00:22:30.920
Buddy, can I borrow your umbrella?

00:22:30.920 --> 00:22:33.320
The stars don't have one over there.

00:22:33.320 --> 00:22:34.793
Thanks.

00:22:39.760 --> 00:22:41.249
Watch your step, Mr. Zhen.

00:22:54.240 --> 00:22:56.440
Gossip news loves to exaggerate.

00:22:56.440 --> 00:22:57.680
Don't pay any mind to it.

00:22:57.680 --> 00:22:59.490
I'll take care of myself.

00:23:01.480 --> 00:23:02.640
Lin.

00:23:02.640 --> 00:23:04.164
Are you nervous?

00:23:06.560 --> 00:23:09.240
Are you and Zhen Xin close?

00:23:09.240 --> 00:23:10.960
Huh?

00:23:10.960 --> 00:23:12.160
No.

00:23:12.160 --> 00:23:15.200
I was just the stunt double for the female lead in his scenes.

00:23:15.200 --> 00:23:16.360
I know that.

00:23:16.360 --> 00:23:17.760
Anything else?

00:23:17.760 --> 00:23:20.280
You haven't offended him, have you?

00:23:20.280 --> 00:23:23.965
Like yelled at him? Or stole his girlfriend?

00:23:24.720 --> 00:23:28.007
Lin... I don't even have him on WeChat.

00:23:30.680 --> 00:23:32.800
Did something happen?

00:23:32.800 --> 00:23:34.925
No, no. I'm just asking.

00:23:37.400 --> 00:23:39.969
Why would he be so kind?

00:23:41.120 --> 00:23:43.440
Listen, remember this.

00:23:43.440 --> 00:23:46.520
Zhen Xin is our company's top star.

00:23:46.520 --> 00:23:48.360
When you're on set, you have to be quick-witted.

00:23:48.360 --> 00:23:49.760
